      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY ULTIMATE BRUNO (8) made a winning start for the Nathan Turnbull yard two runs back before working but sticking on well at his latest appearance at Parkes, coming from this row to be beaten 1.2 metres into second. With better fortune he can return to the winners' list. CAM I AM (9) worked from a similar draw to this at Parkes last start and boxed on for a 3.2m third. That made it back-to-back placings having clocked in second here prior. Race fit now and has the hoof on the till. ULTIMATE COOKIE (5) made it three placings on the trot when second here last week. Go well again. REDUCE SPEED (10) showed improvement second-up and could progress further.",
